data.title: Lenovo Y50 and Y70 Series Gaming Laptops Interview
data.description:
Here’s a Gaming Laptops, made by Lenovo, Y50 and Y70 Series!. Check out the video for more info!

If you’re looking for a laptop that will deliver the ultimate gaming and multimedia experience, look no further. The Lenovo Y50 is a portable gaming powerhouse. The Y50 boasts a Full HD display, the latest Intel® processor, powerful NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960M discrete graphics, JBL® -designed stereo speakers and premium Dolby® Advanced Audio to make it a gamer’s dream machine.

data.description:

3.2Gbps - The fastest combined Wi-Fi speed for uninterrupted streaming
